==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Improvidence
<hw>Im*prov"i*dence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>improvidentia</ets>; OF. <ets>improvidence</ets>. Cf.
<er>Imprudence</er>.]</ety> <def>The quality of being improvident; lack
of foresight or thrift.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>improvidence</qex> of my neighbor must not make me
inhuman.</q> <rj><qau>L'Estrange.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Improvident</ent>⟦br⟧
